This is LittleFS code based on upstream commit c8323112ee535088eb77ab04bfb8a4bb2fe77e30.

The following changes were made:

1.) Adjust #includes to match Linux file names
2.) Fix for loop usage for C89 compliance
3.) Provide malloc / free wrappers in lfs_util.h
4.) Disable a number of features like asserts and logging via lfs_util.h #defines